org.spongepowered.api.event.entity

Interface EntityTeleportEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cancellable, CauseTracked, EntityDisplaceEvent, EntityEvent, Event, GameEvent

    public interface EntityTeleportEvent
extends EntityDisplaceEvent, CauseTracked
    Called when an Entity teleports.

    This is a discrete jump from the old to new location; the entity has not moved between those two places.
